Look what just popped up on the side of our shop! If you haven't heard, @fieldmuseum is hosting an exhibit on the history of tattooing. Tattoo art and artifacts will be on display. On top of that, @fieldmuseum built an actual functioning tattoo shop within the exhibit, and will host guest artists so visitors can witness the tattoo process first hand! Check it out, get inspired, and then visit us for your own tattoo 😊 Fun stuff. #chicago #fieldmuseum #fmtattoo #chicagotattooartist #chicagotattooshops #tattoofm
